This example illustrates:
- how to set up unstructured grid, 
- how to set up field representation defined on that grid, 
- how to evaluate the defined field in a given point,
- how to export field to vtk file

Prerequisites:
--------------
pyvtk python module is required. To install pyvtk, we reccomend to use pip: 
a tool for installing and managing Python packages:

> pip install pyvtk

Note: The pyvtk module requires Python 2.x 

To run the example:

> python Example04.py 


